title: Andy Warstar - 07/24/07 Planet 88 FM
description:
Andy Warstar&#039;s appearance on Planet Radio 88 FM out of Brisbane, Oz (Andy&#039;s

original hometown). Planet 88 FM is the world&#039;s first environmental radio station,

and totally kicks ass! Andy showed up to this performance after a couple other

times trying to find the station. When he finally did show up, he blew into the

studio with a bleached out mohawk under his stitched black woolen cap and busted

out a punkified version of "Imagine" by John Lennon, "Like A Rolling Stone" by

Bob Dylan, and the original tune "Jessie The Dominatrix".
